The functions of the said Committee shall be as follows: -
1) Mahatma Jyotirao Phule Jan Arogya Yojana and Ayushman Bharat Pradhan Mantri Jan Arogya Yojana
Standardization of Adopted Hospital for effective implementation of these schemes.

To give directions in accordance with the giving. State Level, Zonal and District Level Committees
Call for reports and review of health services provided under the scheme; and
To recommend to the Government the measures to be taken accordingly.
(2) The Member-Secretary shall keep a record of the recommendations made by the Committee from time to time and the minutes of the meetings.
They have to be saved.
3. Office / Hall etc. of Ayushman Bharat-Mission Maharashtra Committee to be arranged by CEO, State Health Assurance Society, Worli, Mumbai.
4. The Chairman of the Committee shall be paid such emoluments and facilities as may be permissible under the rules in force.
5. The provisions of the Government Decision dated 28th July, 2023 in reference shall continue.
The Government decision was made available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
